## Rust GPU Crate Stack

```rust
// Cargo.toml - Core GPU dependencies

[dependencies]
# Graphics
wgpu = "0.19"                    # WebGPU (cross-platform)
ash = "0.37"                     # Vulkan bindings
vulkano = "0.34"                 # Safe Vulkan wrapper

# Math
glam = { version = "0.25", features = ["cuda"] }
nalgebra = "0.32"
ultraviolet = "0.9"              # SIMD math

# Physics
parry3d = "0.13"                 # Collision detection
rapier3d = "0.18"                # Physics engine

# Asset Loading
gltf = "1.4"                     # glTF loader
image = "0.24"                   # Image processing
tobj = "4.0"                     # OBJ loader

# AI/ML
candle-core = "0.4"              # Rust ML framework
ort = "2.0"                      # ONNX Runtime

# Serialization
serde = { version = "1.0", features = ["derive"] }
bincode = "1.3"                  # Binary serialization
rmp-serde = "1.1"                # MessagePack

# Async
tokio = { version = "1.35", features = ["full"] }
async-channel = "2.1"

# Networking
tungstenite = "0.21"             # WebSocket
axum = "0.7"                     # HTTP server

[build-dependencies]
spirv-builder = "0.9"            # Compile Rust to SPIR-V
```

## GPU Memory Layout

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      GPU VRAM ALLOCATION (per GPU)                          │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                             │
│  GPU 0: 24GB VRAM                         GPU 1: 24GB VRAM                 │
│  ══════════════════                       ══════════════════               │
│                                                                             │
│  ┌──────────────────────┐                 ┌──────────────────────┐         │
│  │ TINY MODEL           │ 4GB             │ FRAME BUFFERS        │ 2GB     │
│  │ (quantized weights)  │                 │ (triple buffered)    │         │
│  ├──────────────────────┤                 ├──────────────────────┤         │
│  │ KV CACHE             │ 2GB             │ DEPTH/STENCIL        │ 512MB   │
│  │ (context window)     │                 │                      │         │
│  ├──────────────────────┤                 ├──────────────────────┤         │
│  │ TEXTURE GEN          │ 8GB             │ SCENE GEOMETRY       │ 8GB     │
│  │ (SDXL workspace)     │                 │ (vertex/index)       │         │
│  ├──────────────────────┤                 ├──────────────────────┤         │
│  │ MESH GEN             │ 6GB             │ TEXTURES             │ 8GB     │
│  │ (3D model gen)       │                 │ (loaded assets)      │         │
│  ├──────────────────────┤                 ├──────────────────────┤         │
│  │ STAGING              │ 2GB             │ RAY TRACING          │ 4GB     │
│  │ (upload/download)    │                 │ (BVH/acceleration)   │         │
│  ├──────────────────────┤                 ├──────────────────────┤         │
│  │ RESERVED             │ 2GB             │ COMPUTE SCRATCH      │ 1.5GB   │
│  │ (overflow/system)    │                 │ (physics, particles) │         │
│  └──────────────────────┘                 └──────────────────────┘         │
│                                                                             │
│  INTER-GPU TRANSFER: PCIe 4.0 (~25 GB/s bidirectional)                     │
│  ├── Asset streaming (GPU0 gen → GPU1 render)                              │
│  ├── Async copy queues                                                     │
│  └── Pinned system memory staging                                          │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

