# PART 2: GOALS MATRIX

## Complete Project Goals

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         GENTLYOS ECOSYSTEM GOALS                            │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                             │
│  ████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████  │
│  █                                                                        █  │
│  █   MISSION: Sovereignty-first computing where Claude is the             █  │
│  █   primary interface, eliminating traditional desktop environments      █  │
│  █   while giving creators the power to build and ship games              █  │
│  █   to any platform from a phone.                                        █  │
│  █                                                                        █  │
│  ████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████  │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  TIER 1: CORE SYSTEMS (Foundational)                                      ║
╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                                           ║
║  [●] 1.1 CODIE Language                                                   ║
║      ├── 94.7% token compression DSL                                      ║
║      ├── Vector Barf normalization (VB1-VB5)                              ║
║      ├── Hashable, diffable, GPU-agnostic                                 ║
║      ├── Berlin Clock KDF temporal linking                                ║
║      └── XOR cipher for state encryption                                  ║
║                                                                           ║
║  [●] 1.2 BONES/BLOB/BIZ/CIRCLE/PIN Architecture                          ║
║      ├── BONES: Entity structure and behaviors                            ║
║      ├── BLOB: Binary asset containers                                    ║
║      ├── BIZ: I/O protocol layer (the interface)                          ║
║      ├── CIRCLE: Spatial/temporal context                                 ║
║      └── PIN: Identity and provenance                                     ║
║                                                                           ║
║  [●] 1.3 .CDI File Format                                                 ║
║      ├── Universal container for all five atomic types                    ║
║      ├── Hydrates to any game engine                                      ║
║      ├── Blake3 checksums, Ed25519 signatures                             ║
║      └── Compression (LZ4/Zstd)                                           ║
║                                                                           ║
║  [ ] 1.4 Rust 3D Kernel                                                   ║
║      ├── Headless scene graph                                             ║
║      ├── glam math, parry3d collision                                     ║
║      ├── glTF export (Y-up, meters)                                       ║
║      └── MCP socket bridge (port 9876)                                    ║
║                                                                           ║
║  [ ] 1.5 Tiny Local Model (1-3B params)                                   ║
║      ├── Fine-tuned on CODIE syntax                                       ║
║      ├── Semantic → CODIE parsing                                         ║
║      ├── Always running, phone-capable                                    ║
║      └── GGUF quantized (4-bit)                                           ║
║                                                                           ║
╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║  TIER 2: DESIGN STUDIO (The Forward Path)                                 ║
╠═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                                           ║
║  [ ] 2.1 Phone-First UI                                                   ║
║      ├── HTMX (no React bloat)                                            ║
