## Priority Matrix

```
                        IMPACT
                    LOW         HIGH
                ┌───────────┬───────────┐
           HIGH │  QUICK    │  CRITICAL │
                │  WINS     │  PATH     │
    EFFORT      │           │           │
                │  2.2,2.3  │  1.4,1.5  │
                │  4.1      │  2.1,3.1  │
                ├───────────┼───────────┤
           LOW  │  SKIP     │  DO NOW   │
                │  (defer)  │  (done)   │
                │           │           │
                │  3.6,5.3  │  1.1,1.2  │
                │           │  1.3      │
                └───────────┴───────────┘

RECOMMENDED ORDER:
1. [DONE] CODIE Language (1.1)
2. [DONE] BONES/BLOB/BIZ/CIRCLE/PIN (1.2)
3. [DONE] .CDI Format (1.3)
4. [NEXT] Rust 3D Kernel (1.4)
5. [NEXT] Phone UI (2.1)
6. [NEXT] Unity Hydrator (3.1)
7. [THEN] Tiny Model (1.5)
8. [THEN] Other hydrators
9. [THEN] Decompiler
10. [THEN] Collaboration
```

