│   PROTOCOL FEATURES:                                                       │
│                                                                             │
│   • MCP Tools: spawn_entity, modify_entity, get_scene, etc.               │
│   • WebSocket: Real-time sync (port 9876)                                  │
│   • JSON-RPC 2.0: Standard request/response                                │
│   • Value Scaling: Automatic normalization (0-1 ↔ engine scale)           │
│   • Coordinate Transform: Y-up meters ↔ engine-specific                   │
│   • Asset Conversion: .glb ↔ engine-native formats                        │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
